       PROGRAMA SECTION.
       ABRO.
           PERFORM CONF-CAMPOS.
           MOVE 0 TO CLAVE-1-CAP.
       INI-MOD.
           MOVE "GCMODA" TO NOM-PAN.
           OPEN INPUT PANTA.
           READ PANTA WITH NO LOCK.
           CLOSE PANTA.
           MOVE 0 TO SW2 COD-CLAVE.
       PANTA-INI.
           ADD 1 TO SW2.
           IF SW2 > 25 GO TO SIGA-CLAVE.
           DISPLAY LIN-PAN(SW2) LINE SW2 POSITION 1.
           GO TO PANTA-INI.
       SIGA-CLAVE.
           IF CLAVE-1-CAP NOT = 0 GO TO SIGA-INI.
           PERFORM CLAVE-SYS.
           PERFORM BORRA-CLAVE.
       SIGA-INI.
           PERFORM TIT-PAN.
           PERFORM TITU-PAN.
           PERFORM FECHA-PAN.
           PERFORM OPC-MODA.
           PERFORM MEN-MODA-A.
       CARGO-MOD.
           MOVE 28 TO SW3.
           ACCEPT COD1 LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                   ON EXCEPTION EXCEP GO TO TAREAS.
           GO TO CARGO-MOD.
       TAREAS.
           IF ESCAP EXIT PROGRAM
                    STOP RUN.
           IF F01 GO TO ACTU.
           IF F03 GO TO CONS-NUM.
           IF F05 GO TO LIST-NUM.
           GO TO CARGO-MOD.
       ACTU.
           MOVE " ALTA, BAJA Y MODIF " TO D20-CAP.
           PERFORM MODA-PAN
           PERFORM BORRA-PANTA.
       PANTA-ACTU.
           DISPLAY "EMPRESA    :" LINE 7 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "SUC.:      -" LINE 7 POSITION 24. 
           DISPLAY "NRO ENVASE :" LINE 10 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "DETALLE    :" LINE 12 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "CANT.BULTO :" LINE 14 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "CONT.UNIDAD:" LINE 16 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "TIPO CONT. :" LINE 18 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "PESO BULTO :" LINE 20 POSITION 3.
           MOVE SPACES TO MEN-1 MEN-2 MEN-3.
           PERFORM MEN-MODA-S.
           OPEN INPUT EMPRESAS.
           PERFORM CARGA-EMP THRU CARGA-EMP-F.
           CLOSE EMPRESAS.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE1.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 GO TO INI-MOD.
       SIGA-ACTU.
           OPEN INPUT ENVASE.
       CARGA-NUM.
           PERFORM BORRA-PANTA-C.
           MOVE 16 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           PERFORM CAP-NUM.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF NUM-CAP = 0 GO TO CARGA-NUM.
           MOVE NUM-CAP TO NUM-ENVA.
       LEE-ENV.
           READ ENVASE INVALID KEY GO TO ALTA.
           PERFORM DESP-DES THRU DESP-PESO.
           PERFORM MEN-B-M.
           MOVE 28 TO SW3.
           PERFORM CAP-COD1.
           MOVE SPACES TO MEN-1 MEN-2 MEN-3.
           PERFORM MENS-PAN.
           IF ESCAP GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F09 GO TO MODI.
           IF F10 GO TO BAJA.
           GO TO CARGA-NUM.
       ALTA.
           PERFORM MEN-ANTE.
           MOVE 17 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           ACCEPT D20-CAP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                    SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3) NO BEEP TAB
                    ON EXCEPTION EXCEP MOVE SW3 TO SW3.
           MOVE SPACES TO MEN-1 MEN-2 MEN-3.
            PERFORM MENS-PAN.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F02 GO TO CARGA-NUM.
           MOVE D20-CAP TO NOM-ENVA.
       CARGA-CANT1.
           PERFORM MEN-ANTE-DES.
           MOVE 18 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           ACCEPT CANT1-CAP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                             SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3) NO BEEP TAB CONVERT
                             ON EXCEPTION EXCEP MOVE SW3 TO SW3.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F02 GO TO ALTA.
           IF F03 PERFORM DESP-CANT1 GO TO CARGA-CANT2.
           IF CANT1-CAP = 0 GO TO CARGA-CANT1.
           MOVE CANT1-CAP TO CANT1-ENVA.
           PERFORM DESP-CANT1.
       CARGA-CANT2.
           MOVE 19 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           ACCEPT CANT2-CAP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                             SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3) NO BEEP TAB CONVERT
                             ON EXCEPTION EXCEP MOVE SW3 TO SW3.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F02 GO TO CARGA-CANT1.
           IF F03 PERFORM DESP-CANT2 GO TO CARGA-TIPO.
           IF CANT2-CAP = 0 GO TO CARGA-CANT2.
           MOVE CANT2-CAP TO CANT2-ENVA.
           PERFORM DESP-CANT2.
       CARGA-TIPO.
           MOVE 20 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           ACCEPT TIPO-CAP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                           SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3) NO BEEP TAB CONVERT
                           ON EXCEPTION EXCEP MOVE SW3 TO SW3.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F02 GO TO CARGA-CANT2.
           IF F03 PERFORM DESP-TIPO GO TO CARGA-PESO.
           MOVE TIPO-CAP TO TIPO-ENVA.
           PERFORM DESP-TIPO.
       CARGA-PESO.
           MOVE 21 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           ACCEPT PESO-CAP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                           SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3) NO BEEP TAB CONVERT
                           ON EXCEPTION EXCEP MOVE SW3 TO SW3.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F02 GO TO CARGA-TIPO.
           IF F03 PERFORM DESP-PESO GO TO GRAVO.
           MOVE PESO-CAP TO PESO-ENVA.
           PERFORM DESP-PESO.
       GRAVO.
           CLOSE ENVASE.
           OPEN I-O ENVASE.
           WRITE REG-ENVASE INVALID KEY REWRITE REG-ENVASE.
           CLOSE ENVASE.
           OPEN INPUT ENVASE.
           GO TO CARGA-NUM.
       BAJA.
           PERFORM MEN-CONF.
           MOVE 28 TO SW3.
           PERFORM CAP-COD1.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE2.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE3.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F01 CLOSE ENVASE
                  OPEN I-O ENVASE
                  DELETE ENVASE 
                  CLOSE ENVASE
                  OPEN INPUT ENVASE
                  MOVE SPACES TO MEN-1 MEN-2 MEN-3
                  PERFORM MENS-PAN
                  UNLOCK ENVASE RECORD
                  GO TO CARGA-NUM.
           PERFORM MEN-NO-BAJA.
           MOVE SPACES TO MEN-1 MEN-2 MEN-3.
           PERFORM MENS-PAN.
           UNLOCK ENVASE RECORD.
           GO TO CARGA-NUM.
       MODI.
           PERFORM DESP-DES THRU DESP-PESO.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE2.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE3.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           UNLOCK ENVASE RECORD.
           PERFORM ALTA THRU CARGA-PESO.
           GO TO CARGA-NUM.
       CONS-NUM.
           PERFORM MEN-MODA-S.
           PERFORM BORRA-PANTA.
           MOVE 1 TO SW3.
           MOVE "CONSULTA NUMERICA" TO D20-CAP.
           PERFORM MODA-PAN.
           PERFORM PANTA-ACTU.
           OPEN INPUT ENVASE.
       C-N-DESDE.
           PERFORM BORRA-PANTA-C.
           PERFORM MEN-F-CONS.
           MOVE 16 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           PERFORM CAP-NUM.
           IF F01 CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF NUM-CAP = 0 GO TO C-N-DESDE.
           MOVE NUM-CAP TO NUM-ENVA.
           START ENVASE KEY IS NOT < CLAVE-ENVASE
                      INVALID KEY GO TO C-N-DESDE.
       C-N-SIGO.
           READ ENVASE NEXT WITH NO LOCK AT END GO TO C-N-DESDE.
           MOVE 16 TO SW3.
           DISPLAY NUM-ENVA LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                            SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3).
           PERFORM DESP-DES THRU DESP-PESO.
           MOVE 28 TO SW3.
           PERFORM MEN-CONS.
           PERFORM CAP-COD1.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE ENVASE GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F03 GO TO C-N-SIGO.
           GO TO C-N-DESDE.
       LIST-NUM.
           PERFORM BORRA-PANTA.
           PERFORM MEN-MODA-S.
           MOVE 1 TO SW3.
           MOVE " LISTADO NUMERICO " TO D20-CAP.
           PERFORM MODA-PAN.
           DISPLAY "EMPRESA   :" LINE 7 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "SUC.:       -" LINE 7 POSITION 24.
           DISPLAY "DESDE: " LINE 9 POSITION 3.
           DISPLAY "HASTA: " LINE 9 POSITION 40.
           OPEN INPUT EMPRESAS.
           PERFORM CARGA-EMP THRU CARGA-EMP-F.
           CLOSE EMPRESAS.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE1.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 GO TO INI-MOD.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE2.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 GO TO INI-MOD.
           PERFORM CHEQUEA-CLAVE3.
           IF COD-CLAVE = 9 GO TO INI-MOD.
       L-N-DESDE.
           MOVE 3 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           PERFORM CAP-NUM.
           IF ESCAP  GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F01  GO TO INI-MOD.
           MOVE NUM-CAP TO LISTO-D NUM-ENVA.
       L-N-HASTA.
           PERFORM MEN-ANTE.
           MOVE 4 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           PERFORM CAP-NUM.
           IF ESCAP GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F02 GO TO L-N-DESDE.
           MOVE NUM-CAP TO LISTO-H.
           MOVE "N" TO COD2.
       L-N-POSI.
           OPEN OUTPUT IMP01.
           OPEN INPUT ENVASE.
           START ENVASE KEY IS NOT < CLAVE-ENVASE
                        INVALID KEY CLOSE ENVASE IMP01
                        GO TO L-N-DESDE.
           MOVE "N" TO COD2.
           MOVE SPACES TO COD3.
           MOVE 0 TO CONT-P CONT-I CONT-R.
           MOVE SPACES TO TIT-1-EDI TIT-6-EDI.
           MOVE " <<< LISTA" TO TIT-2-EDI.
           MOVE "DO NUMERIC" TO TIT-3-EDI.
           MOVE "O DE ENVAS" TO TIT-4-EDI.
           MOVE "ES  >>>   " TO TIT-5-EDI.
           MOVE TITULO-EDI TO TIT-E80.
           PERFORM MEN-LIS.
           GO TO L-LEO.
       L-LEO.
           IF CONT-R = 0 PERFORM TITU.
           IF CONT-R = 68 PERFORM ESPA 4 TIMES
                          MOVE 0 TO CONT-R
                          PERFORM TITU.
           PERFORM LEO-ENVA.
           IF COD2 = "N" AND NUM-ENVA > LISTO-H MOVE "F" TO COD3.
           IF COD3 = "F" PERFORM PIE-P
                         CLOSE IMP01 ENVASE
                         IF COD2 = "N" GO TO L-N-DESDE.
           MOVE NUM-ENVA TO NUME-ED.
           MOVE NOM-ENVA TO NOM-ED.
           MOVE CANT1-ENVA TO CANT1-ED.
           MOVE CANT2-ENVA TO CANT2-ED.
           MOVE TIPO-ENVA TO TIPO-ED.
           MOVE PESO-ENVA TO PESO-ED.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM IMP-3 AFTER ADVANCING 1.
           ADD 1 TO CONT-R.
           ADD 1 TO CONT-I.
           GO TO L-LEO.
       TITU.
           ADD 1 TO CONT-P.
           MOVE 0 TO CONT-R.
           MOVE CONT-P TO HOJ-E80.
           MOVE ANO TO AA-E80.
           MOVE MES TO MM-E80.
           MOVE DIA TO DD-E80.
           ACCEPT TIEMPO FROM TIME.
           MOVE HORA TO HH-E80.
           MOVE MINU TO MI-E80.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-1 AFTER 1.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-3 AFTER 1.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-4 AFTER 1.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-5 AFTER 1.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-1 AFTER 1.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-2 AFTER 1.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM IMP-1 AFTER 1.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-2 AFTER 1.
           ADD 8 TO CONT-R.
       ESPA.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM ROT80-2 AFTER 1.
           ADD 1 TO CONT-R.
       PIE-P.
           PERFORM ESPA.
           MOVE CONT-I TO CONT-L-ED.
           WRITE LIN-IMP01 FROM IMP-2 AFTER 1.
           ADD 1 TO CONT-R.
           COMPUTE CONT-R = 72 - CONT-R.
           PERFORM ESPA CONT-R TIMES.
       LEO-ENVA.
           READ ENVASE NEXT WITH NO LOCK AT END MOVE "F" TO COD3.
       CONF-CAMPOS.
           MOVE 045125 TO TAB-POS(1).
           MOVE 250275 TO TAB-POS(2).
           MOVE 091020 TO TAB-POS(3).
           MOVE 094720 TO TAB-POS(4).
           MOVE 102503 TO TAB-POS(5).
           MOVE 112503 TO TAB-POS(6).
           MOVE 122503 TO TAB-POS(7).
           MOVE 132503 TO TAB-POS(8).
           MOVE 142503 TO TAB-POS(9).
           MOVE 152503 TO TAB-POS(10).
           MOVE 162503 TO TAB-POS(11).
           MOVE 172503 TO TAB-POS(12)
           MOVE 182503 TO TAB-POS(13).
           MOVE 192503 TO TAB-POS(14).
           MOVE 255801 TO TAB-POS(15)
           MOVE 101503 TO TAB-POS(16).
           MOVE 121520 TO TAB-POS(17).
           MOVE 141508 TO TAB-POS(18).
           MOVE 161509 TO TAB-POS(19).
           MOVE 181502 TO TAB-POS(20).
           MOVE 201509 TO TAB-POS(21).
           MOVE 143320 TO TAB-POS(22).
           MOVE 153320 TO TAB-POS(23).
           MOVE 163320 TO TAB-POS(24).
           MOVE 173320 TO TAB-POS(25).
           MOVE 183320 TO TAB-POS(26).
           MOVE 193320 TO TAB-POS(27).
           MOVE 254101 TO TAB-POS(28).
           MOVE 071504 TO TAB-POS(29).
           MOVE 073002 TO TAB-POS(30).
           MOVE 073830 TO TAB-POS(31).
       TIT-PAN.
           MOVE "     -ARCH" TO TIT-1-PAN.
           MOVE "IVO DE ENV" TO TIT-2-PAN.
           MOVE "ASES-     " TO TIT-3-PAN.
       OPC-MODA.
           DISPLAY "<F1>  ALTA,BAJA Y MODIF." LINE 14 POSITION 18.
           DISPLAY "<F3>  CONSULTA NUMERICA " LINE 15 POSITION 18.
           DISPLAY "<F5>  LISTADO NUMERICO  " LINE 16 POSITION 18.
           DISPLAY "<ESC> VUELVE AL MENU   " LINE 17 POSITION 18.
       CARGA-EMP.
           MOVE 31 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE 30 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE 29 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           PERFORM CAP-NUM.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE EMPRESAS GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF NUM-CAP = 0 GO TO CARGA-EMP.
           MOVE NUM-CAP TO NUM-EMP.
           MOVE 0 TO SUC-EMP.
           READ EMPRESAS WITH NO LOCK INVALID KEY GO TO CARGA-EMP.
           MOVE 31 TO SW3.
           DISPLAY RAZ-SOC-EMP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                      SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3).
           MOVE RAZ-SOC-EMP TO EMP-E80.
       CARGA-SUC.
           MOVE 30 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           PERFORM CAP-NUM.
           IF ESCAP CLOSE EMPRESAS GO TO INI-MOD.
           IF F02 GO TO CARGA-EMP.
           MOVE NUM-CAP TO SUC-EMP  NUM-SUC-E80.
           READ EMPRESAS WITH NO LOCK INVALID KEY GO TO CARGA-SUC.
           MOVE 31 TO SW3.
           DISPLAY RAZ-SOC-EMP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                       SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3).
           MOVE RAZ-SOC-EMP TO SUC-E80.
       CARGA-EMP-F.
           EXIT.
       DESP-DES.
           MOVE 17 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE NOM-ENVA TO D20-CAP.
           DISPLAY D20-CAP LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                    SIZE   TAB-SIZ(SW3).
       DESP-CANT1.
           MOVE 18 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE CANT1-ENVA TO CANT1-EDI.
           DISPLAY CANT1-EDI LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                             SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3).
       DESP-CANT2.
           MOVE 19 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE CANT2-ENVA TO CANT2-EDI.
           DISPLAY CANT2-EDI LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                             SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3).
       DESP-TIPO.
           MOVE 20 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE TIPO-ENVA TO TIPO-EDI.
           DISPLAY TIPO-EDI LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                            SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3).
       DESP-PESO.
           MOVE 21 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE PESO-ENVA TO PESO-EDI.
           DISPLAY PESO-EDI LINE TAB-LIN(SW3) POSITION TAB-COL(SW3)
                            SIZE TAB-SIZ(SW3).
       BORRA-PANTA.
           MOVE 0 TO SW1.
           PERFORM BORRA-P1 VARYING SW1 FROM 6 BY 1
                            UNTIL SW1 > 23.
       BORRA-PANTA-C.
           MOVE 16 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE 17 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE 18 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE 19 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE 20 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
           MOVE 21 TO SW3.
           PERFORM BORRA.
       BORRA-P1.
           DISPLAY SPACES LINE SW1 POSITION 2 SIZE 76.
